Author: needmoney
Title: [ANN] flyCARE - Medical, wellness and personal care accessible to everyone.
Body: Medical, wellness and personal care accessible to everyone, anytime, anywhere in the world. It is no longer a utopia. This is flyCARE’s  vision.   The platform aims to be a solution of easy access to services, an all-in -one offer that includes a wide range of services: a physiotherapist, a hairdresser, a dentist, a pedicure specialist for example - all of that at home, simply. flyCARE aims to "fly" (fly) to the client service, offering, through an all- in-one solution and local, motivated and ready service providers, a range of services (CARE) combining comfort, ergonomics and technology.  BRUNO LAMOUREUX, FOUNDER AND CEO, FLYCARE
